MM0085*
MM0085*  IF THE CLIENT HAS ONLY ONE OF 30-DAY TYPE AND C-TYPE THEN 
MM0085*  ADD THE RELEVANT FACE AMOUNT
MM0085*
MM0085*  ELSE
MM0085*
MM0085*  IF THE CLIENT HAS BOTH 30-DAY TYPE AND C-TYPE THEN WE HAVE TO  
MM0085*  DECIDE WHICH AMOUNT (IF ANY) TO SEND AS FOLLOWS:
MM0085*
MM0085*   IF THE COVERAGES WERE ISSUED ON THE SAME DATE SEND THE LARGER
MM0085*
MM0085*   IF THE COVERAGES WERE ISSUED ON DIFFERENT DATES THEN IF THE
