PR006C*
PR006C* IF A C-TYPE RIDER EXISTS IN CONJUNCTION WITH THE ADULT DISEASE
PR006C* RIDER THEN USE THE GREATER OF THE C-TYPE RIDER FACE AMOUNT
PR006C* OR THE 30 DAY RIDER
PR006C*
MM0085*PR006C     IF WS-TOT-HOSP-ADULT-DIS-AMT = ZERO
MM0085*PR006C        MOVE WS-TMP-HOSP-ADIS30-AMT 
MM0085*PR006C        TO   WS-TOT-HOSP-ADULT-DIS-AMT
