MM0085*PR006C           MOVE WS-TMP-HOSP-C-ADIS-AMT 
MM0085*PR006C           TO   WS-TOT-HOSP-ADULT-DIS-AMT
MM0085*PR006C        END-IF
MM0085*PR006C     END-IF.
MM0085*
MM0085* 30-DAY TYPE AND C-TYPE PROCESSING...
MM0085*
MM0085*  IF THE CLIENT HAS ONLY ONE OF 30-DAY TYPE AND C-TYPE THEN 
MM0085*  ADD THE RELEVANT FACE AMOUNT
MM0085*
MM0085*  ELSE
MM0085*
MM0085*  IF THE CLIENT HAS BOTH 30-DAY TYPE AND C-TYPE THEN WE HAVE TO  
MM0085*  DECIDE WHICH AMOUNT (IF ANY) TO SEND AS FOLLOWS:
MM0085*
MM0085*   IF THE COVERAGES WERE ISSUED ON THE SAME DATE SEND THE LARGER
MM0085*
MM0085*   IF THE COVERAGES WERE ISSUED ON DIFFERENT DATES THEN IF THE
MM0085*   NEW COVERAGE IS GREATER THAN THE OLD COVERAGE THEN SEND THE
MM0085*   NEW COVERAGE
MM0085*
MM0085     IF WS-HOSP-ADIS30-CVG-ISS-EFF-DT = SPACES 
MM0085     OR WS-HOSP-C-ADIS-CVG-ISS-EFF-DT = SPACES 
